  "body": "**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**\r\nSometimes it happens that a state requested during block processing is not found and need to be restored. Recovery should be applied to restore enough state for the block to be processed.\r\n\r\n**Describe the solution you'd like**\r\nThe block processor may stop for short amount of time, state nodes (or codes) needed should be downloaded and the block should be re-run.\r\n\r\n**Describe alternatives you've considered**\r\nFallback to synchronization from healthy status and restore all the state.\r\n\r\n**Additional context**\r\nThe recovery should not be done for erroneously requested non-existent state.\r\n",
